74
00:06:03,310 --> 00:06:04,800
(I can't lose her.)

75
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:10,630
Master.

76
00:06:12,740 --> 00:06:14,660
(Mr. Zhou, butler of the Lu family)

77
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:15,240
Master.

78
00:06:22,510 --> 00:06:24,040
How is the kidnap investigation going?

79
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:26,920
The investigation is thorough.
It's not an outsider's job.

80
00:06:27,870 --> 00:06:29,070
Has Zhang Rong come back?

81
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,510
Stop beating me!

82
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:43,240
Darling, I beg you to stop it!

83
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:47,240
Stop beating me, darling!

84
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:49,160
I beg you to stop it!

85
00:06:49,270 --> 00:06:50,430
Keep beating her if she doesn't confess.

86
00:06:50,830 --> 00:06:51,680
Darling,

87
00:06:52,070 --> 00:06:54,160
I do hate Su Kenian.

88
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:56,870
But I only dare to attack her orally.

89
00:06:57,750 --> 00:06:59,950
How dare I pay someone to kidnap her?

90
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:02,270
