91
00:07:04,430 --> 00:07:05,240
Darling,

92
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:07,000
I beg you to stop beating me!

93
00:07:07,190 --> 00:07:08,000
I am not the culprit.

94
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:08,720
Darling!

95
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:09,800
Darling!

96
00:07:10,190 --> 00:07:11,600
