after all these years,

101
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:21,000
I didn't bear you

102
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:23,630
any, any children.

103
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,720
However, I have been your wife
for many years,

104
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,120
I should be given credit

105
00:07:29,630 --> 00:07:31,830
