for the Chamber of Commerce.

108
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:39,600
Why do I deserve

109
00:07:40,190 --> 00:07:43,870
such, such treatment?

110
00:07:45,950 --> 00:07:47,560
Master, I beg you to stop!

111
00:07:47,830 --> 00:07:48,430
If,

112
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:50,920
if you continue,
my mistress will die.

113
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:51,480
Master!

114
00:07:51,510 --> 00:07:52,160
Brother,

115
00:07:53,390 --> 00:07:54,680
she doesn't seem to be
the culprit.

116
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,680
Why do you have the cheek to say that?

117
00:07:58,950 --> 00:08:01,160
I asked you to watch Lu Yichuan
go aboard the ship.

118
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:01,950
However, you failed.

119
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:03,120
If I had stopped Yichuan,

120
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:06,190
Su Kenian would have died.

121
00:08:22,270 --> 00:08:22,920
Mistress.

122
00:08:32,270 --> 00:08:33,320
Su Kenian!

123
00:08:39,390 --> 00:08:40,870
Since I was born,

124
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:45,720
I have never suffered like this.

125
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:49,440
You won't heard

126
00:08:54,550 --> 00:08:57,150
