♪The satirical longing passes by♪

165
00:12:32,060 --> 00:12:35,820
♪I struggle to break free from its grip♪

166
00:12:35,820 --> 00:12:39,500
♪You even take away my happiness♪

167
00:12:39,500 --> 00:12:43,060
♪Where else can I escape?♪

168
00:12:43,060 --> 00:12:48,540
♪Memories occupy
the very last corner of my mind♪

169
00:12:48,540 --> 00:12:51,580
♪Don't make me remember♪

170
00:12:51,580 --> 00:12:53,500
♪Until this day♪

171
00:12:53,900 --> 00:12:57,500
♪I was deeply loved by you♪
